OL,3,CTwo of Wales' fire services face
OL,4,Cbruising report ` but how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FOn Wednesday morning, reports by
OL,8,Findependent investigators revealed
OL,9,F'widespread' issues of bullying and
OL,10,Fharassment in two of Wales' fire
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FThe bruising reports about the culture
OL,14,Fat North and Mid & West Wales Fire and
OL,15,FRescue Services found gender-based
OL,16,Fdiscrimination, as well as bias and
OL,17,Ffavouritism, to be prevailing issues.
