OL,4,Cbruising report ` but how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FAlthough the report into North Wales
OL,8,FService acknowledged some improvements
OL,9,Fin culture, more than two-fifths (42%)
OL,10,Fof survey respondents reported
OL,11,Fpersonal experiences of bullying and
OL,12,Fharassment since June 2021.
OL,14,FThey also described feeling "unsafe"
OL,15,Fdue to "abusive, confrontational"
OL,16,Fsenior leaders.
OL,18,FSevere criticism was levelled at the
OL,19,FMid and West Wales service, due to
OL,20,Fgender-based discrimination and sexism.
