OL,4,Cbruising report ` but how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FIn 2023, ITV News heard how two
OL,8,Ffirefighters at the South Wales
OL,9,Fservice had kept their jobs after
OL,10,Ffacing accusations of sexual
OL,11,Fharassment whilst at work.
OL,13,FThe revelations led to the service
OL,14,Fcommissioning an independent review of
OL,15,Fthe culture there. The review was
OL,16,Ftasked with investigating the
OL,17,Fexperience of staff working in South
OL,18,FWales Fire and Rescue Service.
