OL,7,FWhen the independent report was
OL,8,Fpublished in January 2024, its
OL,9,Ffindings were damning.
OL,11,FFenella Morris KC's report found that
OL,12,Fbullying and harassment at the service
OL,13,Fsometimes went unchallenged and
OL,14,Funpunished.
OL,16,FThe review said it encountered
OL,17,Fevidence of racism, homophobia and
OL,18,Fmisogyny.
