OL,7,FOne former staff member at Mid and
OL,8,FWest Wales Fire said he had seen
OL,9,Fcolleagues "breaking down in tears"
OL,10,Fafter being bullied.
OL,12,FHe said the service "is run like a
OL,13,Fprivate members' club". Many of the
OL,14,Fstaff members we spoke to called for
OL,15,Fan independent review of the fire
OL,16,Fservices, the same as the South Wales
OL,17,Freview. They told us it would be the
OL,18,Fonly way they could raise their
OL,19,Fconcerns.
