OL,7,FWhen we approached the fire services
OL,8,Ffor interviews with their CFOs, we
OL,9,Fwere told they weren't available. In
OL,10,Ffact, throughout our investigation, we
OL,11,Fasked the chief in North Wales, Dawn
OL,12,FDocx, for an interview more than ten
OL,13,Ftimes ` each time our request was
OL,14,Fturned down.
OL,16,FWe managed to speak to the CFO Dawn
OL,17,FDocx about the allegations on the
OL,18,Fsteps of the Senedd.
OL,20,FShe told us, "If (staff) really feel
OL,21,Fthat way, I want to hear from them."
