OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FMs Blythyn said both organisations
OL,8,F"have embarked on comprehensive
OL,9,Fprogrammes to review and improve their
OL,10,Forganisational cultures". Both fire
OL,11,Fchiefs welcomed the announcement of
OL,12,Freviews.
OL,14,FThe reviews were initially expected to
OL,15,Fbe published in the Autumn of 2024,
OL,16,Fhowever, that date was pushed back to
OL,17,FJanuary 2025.
OL,19,FBoth fire services appointed an
OL,20,Findependent body to carry out the
OL,21,Fcultural reviews.
