OL,4,Cbruising report ` but how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FNorth Wales Fire Service described
OL,8,FCrest Advisory's review as "a
OL,9,Fwatershed moment" as CFO Dawn Docx
OL,10,Fapologised in a statement to "those
OL,11,Fwho have not had a good experience."
OL,13,FShe said: "Our staff have asked for
OL,14,Fchange, and we are listening. We
OL,15,Fappreciate their courage in providing
OL,16,Fhonest feedback. They have recognised
OL,17,Fthe improvements already made but
OL,18,Freflect that we still have some way to
OL,19,Fgo.
