OL,7,F"This review marks a watershed moment
OL,8,Ffor us and I want to say sorry to
OL,9,Fthose who have not had a good
OL,10,Fexperience ` everybody deserves to
OL,11,Ffeel heard, safe and valued in their
OL,12,Fworkplace."
OL,14,FMid and West Wales Service's Chief
OL,15,FFire Officer Roger Thomas also
OL,16,Fexpressed regret, and said he
OL,17,Fapologises "unreservedly" to
OL,18,Fcolleagues who have been subject to
OL,19,F"bullying, harassment or
OL,20,Fdiscrimination in any form."
