OL,7,FThe minister in charge of the Fire
OL,8,FServices, Jayne Bryant MS, said in a
OL,9,Fstatement that she has met with the
OL,10,FChairs of both Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FAuthorities and both Chief Fire
OL,12,FOfficers to discuss how they plan to
OL,13,Faddress the reports' findings.
OL,15,FShe said: "During these meetings I set
OL,16,Fout my expectation that clear and
OL,17,Fdecisive action should be taken
OL,18,Fimmediately to dismantle these
OL,19,Fdamaging cultures and ensure staff
OL,20,Ffeel safe and valued in their
OL,21,Fworkplace.
