OL,12,Fand urgently work to establish how
OL,13,Fbest to achieve and sustain cultural
OL,14,Fchange across the Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FService.
OL,17,F"I will make a further statement to
OL,18,Fthe Senedd on these issues, and about
